# AI Workflow ROI Calculator

This project explores a simple way to estimate the potential return from automating workflow tasks with AI.

## Problem

Organizations often struggle to estimate the value of AI automation before building a system.  
This calculator provides a simple framework to model potential savings.

## Inputs

- Number of tasks per day
- Average time per task
- Percentage of tasks that can be automated
- Cost per hour of labor

## Output

Estimated:

- time savings
- cost savings
- productivity gains

## Why I Built This

I work on AI-driven workflow products and often need a quick way to reason about the economic value of automation.

This project is a lightweight prototype to explore those calculations.

## Future Ideas

- web interface
- scenario comparisons
- integration with workflow analytics
